    "stat_block": {
        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "This *+1 striking hauling longbow* is lined with the flesh of a fallen hydra and ornate carvings on the grip that depict the hydra\u2019s number of heads it had before it was slain. When you wield the bow in combat, you regain 2 Hit Points at the start of each of your turns.",
